{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-js","path":"/ubuntu-smb/","result":{"data":{"remark":{"fields":{"path":"ubuntu-smb"},"meta":{"title":""},"headings":[{"value":"Ubuntu SMB"},{"value":"Configure persistent mounting"},{"value":"Mount everything"},{"value":"Unmount share"}],"html":"<h1>Ubuntu SMB</h1>\n<h2>Install required software</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> cifs-utils</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Create folders where mounting will happen</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> /root/desktop\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> /root/d\n<span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> ~/desktop\n<span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> ~/d</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Credentials</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">cat</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token string\">EOF<span class=\"token bash punctuation\"> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">tee</span> /root/.smbcredentials</span>\nusername=AlexandrM\npassword=xxxxxxxxxx\nEOF</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">chmod</span> <span class=\"token number\">600</span> /root/.smbcredentials</code></pre></div>\n<h1>Configure persistent mounting</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo<